      "content": "That doesn't quite sit right with me. I've seen the satellite imagery from the last 48 hours, and those 'routine exercises' don't usually involve mobile missile batteries positioning themselves in forward deployment zones. If this is just a logistical test, why are the field commanders requesting immediate readiness status? Is there anything in the recent signal intelligence that might contradict the 'joint exercise' narrative?",
